ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

978
00:53:02,868 --> 00:53:04,501
CERTAINLY, NO GENTLEMAN IN THE ACADEMY

979
00:53:04,567 --> 00:53:05,901
COULD DENY THE REQUEST OF LADIES,

980
00:53:05,968 --> 00:53:07,501
